title: Steely Dan - Studio, Rare & Live Album Collection
description:
Steely Dan...
..A sort-of discography

Here is my collection of Steely Dan albums.
Most of these rips I did myself from my personal collection.
Some have been pulled off trader sites & other torrents (now dead links)


This collection includes: 
  Every studio album from Steely Dan, Donald Fagen & Walter Becker
  All album outtakes & unreleased / unfinished tracks
  A large selection of live shows spanning 1973 - 2012


Files are either MP3 or FLAC. 
Most MP3s are 320k, others are 128k or 192k CBR.

There are a few live shows I have recorded myself using an MP3 recorder (not the best of quality).

A couple different versions of a few live show remasters are also included for your consideration. A few are incomplete shows I have put together from old services such as Napster, LimeWire & BearShare.

Don't miss the studio outtakes & instrumentals... Absolutely delicious.


I hope you enjoy this collection :)


[] Cubilas 2014 []
